                <p class="text-gray-600">Choose from a variety of insurance plans that fit your budget.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
                <i class="fas fa-phone-alt text-blue-700 text-4xl mb-4"></i>
                <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold">24/7 Support</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Our support team is available anytime you need assistance.</p>
